  "Description": "This UiPath project demonstrates how to use the App/Web Recorder to automate a complete loan application process in a web browser.\nThe automation opens the UiBank Loan website, fills in required details, submits the application, extracts the generated Loan ID, and displays it in a message box.",
  "MainFile": "Main.xaml"
}